Executive Summary 3

Problems that occurred during the project:

1.While executing the SSIS package one column was not recognized so it threw an error. We had to go back into the SSMS and made sure the column names were harmonized.

2.While Executing the SSIS package, it threw an error that the subquery was returning more than one value. When we checked in the Excel source Somali was in 2 regions. So, we Corrected the region as Africa, and we were able to run the package successfully.
